03:18.721 --> 03:20.311
-Is she yours now?

03:21.549 --> 03:22.682
-Why are you here?

03:25.151 --> 03:27.789
Things would have been very
different if it weren't for her.

03:28.349 --> 03:30.553
(gentle music)

03:30.577 --> 03:32.577
(gentle music)

03:32.601 --> 03:34.601
(gentle music)

03:38.124 --> 03:39.124
Thank you.

03:40.641 --> 03:42.690
- [Theodore]-So...
- [Helen]- So...

03:42.714 --> 03:44.714
- Good news.
- Okay.

03:44.738 --> 03:48.268
Your eggs have been successfully
fertilized with your late husband's sperm.

03:49.110 --> 03:52.377
You requested twins.
We have even better news.

03:52.698 --> 03:54.098
Identical twin girls.

03:55.276 --> 03:58.503
- I don't know how to thank you.
- Oh, don't thank me.

03:58.527 --> 04:02.201
Identical twins are still God's creation
and we're not quite there yet, but

04:02.484 --> 04:04.284
It's only a matter of time.

04:04.391 --> 04:06.991
Michael would - he would be so pleased.

04:11.117 --> 04:13.376
I just want to prepare
you for this, but

04:14.086 --> 04:17.675
It seems your girls have inherited your
husband's gene for cardiac hypertrophy.

04:17.699 --> 04:20.664
- He died at 35.
- I realize that.

04:21.147 --> 04:23.103
Our company has a
solution for this.

04:23.491 --> 04:26.192
Have you heard of the
Universal Genome Program?

04:26.327 --> 04:28.660
A few samples of blood,
skin and saliva...

04:28.685 --> 04:30.366
Yeah, I know what this is.

04:30.592 --> 04:33.881
By matching their genetic profiles
with the millions on our database,

04:34.162 --> 04:36.162
we can predict their medical destiny,

04:36.615 --> 04:40.148
and soon technology will allow
us to repair their future.

04:44.669 --> 04:45.669
Doctor?

04:46.296 --> 04:47.296
(eerie music)

04:48.141 --> 04:49.741
Doctor, are you alright?

04:49.765 --> 04:51.765
(eerie music)

04:51.789 --> 04:53.789
(eerie music)

04:55.391 --> 04:56.391
[water running]

05:01.796 --> 05:02.996
Shall I take over?

05:17.579 --> 05:18.712
How are we doing?

05:23.093 --> 05:24.018
-How is she?

05:24.043 --> 05:26.126
-Not looking good.

05:27.054 --> 05:30.587
Her doctor loses it in the
middle of her examination.

05:30.611 --> 05:34.633
- It's not what you think.
- Let me run your junk through the program.

05:35.079 --> 05:39.868
With my code. I could easily
find you similar genetic profiles-

05:39.892 --> 05:41.055
Walter!

05:42.642 --> 05:43.642
Enough.

05:47.780 --> 05:49.414
You won't find me in the program.

05:52.178 --> 05:53.686
- What do you mean?

05:53.711 --> 05:57.679
Every employee submits their
genome to the program.

05:59.296 --> 06:00.629
-I'm not an employee.

06:35.334 --> 06:36.334
(gentle music)

06:38.020 --> 06:39.754
Something's bothering you.

06:46.012 --> 06:47.012
-It's a patient.

06:48.592 --> 06:49.858
-It's bad news, huh?

06:52.240 --> 06:53.440
Have you told her?

06:56.118 --> 06:58.125
-No, it's fine.

07:05.923 --> 07:07.056
(phone vibrating)

07:08.970 --> 07:09.970
(phone vibrating)

07:18.007 --> 07:19.007
- Hello?

07:20.864 --> 07:21.864
Yeah.

07:30.739 --> 07:33.206
Hey, hold on, I got to get a pen.

07:39.006 --> 07:40.006
Okay.

07:44.092 --> 07:45.892
Uh-huh, I know where it is.

07:47.674 --> 07:48.674
What time?

07:50.901 --> 07:51.901
Okay.

07:53.120 --> 07:54.120
Helen,

07:56.393 --> 07:58.326
Don't forget what I said yesterday.

08:14.545 --> 08:16.255
-Hi, good morning.

08:17.162 --> 08:18.162
Hey.

08:21.537 --> 08:24.153
- What are you doing?
- Who was that?

08:25.069 --> 08:27.880
- It was Walter.
- It's Walter? It's Saturday.

08:27.904 --> 08:30.470
- He's a workaholic. Mm-hmm.
- Mm-hmm...

08:30.495 --> 08:31.758
What are you doing
in my robe, huh?

08:31.783 --> 08:34.770
You haven't asked me to move in yet.
I have no clothes.

08:37.515 --> 08:40.020
(phone vibrating)

08:40.044 --> 08:42.044
(phone vibrating)

08:43.113 --> 08:44.113
- Hey, Em.

08:45.488 --> 08:47.449
<i>- [Emma] He's flying back
from London tonight.</i>

08:47.474 --> 08:49.058
<i>I don't know what
is going to happen.</i>

08:49.722 --> 08:50.922
<i>I'm really scared.</i>

08:57.646 --> 08:59.091
(car engine)

