23:48.780 --> 23:49.780
(eerie music)

24:06.192 --> 24:07.192
-[Theodore] Anna?

24:14.737 --> 24:15.937
- She was my sister.

24:19.245 --> 24:20.245
- Emma.

24:23.790 --> 24:24.790
Of course.

24:31.899 --> 24:32.899
How are you?

24:35.376 --> 24:36.509
-I'm alright.

24:38.869 --> 24:39.869
(sighs)

24:48.830 --> 24:51.582
You knew there was going to be a
shooting that night, didn't you?

24:57.391 --> 24:59.125
-I didn't know she'd show up.

25:02.294 --> 25:03.294
(gentle music)

25:09.485 --> 25:10.485
(gentle music)

25:22.168 --> 25:23.168
Emma.

25:27.652 --> 25:29.252
- It was nice meeting you.

25:29.397 --> 25:31.790
(heartbeat)

25:33.718 --> 25:34.718
- Whoa.

25:36.374 --> 25:37.374
Are you okay?

25:39.054 --> 25:40.054
What's wrong?

25:42.608 --> 25:46.141
- If it wasn't for you, my
sister would still be alive.

25:49.608 --> 25:51.941
-[Theodore] Seeing her felt
like Anna survived.

25:53.733 --> 25:55.266
- But she didn't survive.

25:57.436 --> 25:59.436
Where are you going with this?

26:01.749 --> 26:02.904
What did she want?

26:03.517 --> 26:05.239
- [Theodore] She didn't say. She just left.

26:08.007 --> 26:09.789
-[Aunt Kay] Something
is not right.

26:10.470 --> 26:11.499
- What do you mean?

26:13.113 --> 26:15.430
- [Aunt Kay] You never
even met her sister,

26:15.455 --> 26:17.147
and suddenly she appears?

26:17.171 --> 26:19.171
-[Theodore] That's why I followed her.

26:22.091 --> 26:23.802
-[Helen]- Hey.
- [Emma]-Hey.

26:23.826 --> 26:26.302
- Sorry I'm horribly late.
I'm sorry.

26:28.474 --> 26:30.007
- [Aunt Kay] Why are you doing this?

26:33.156 --> 26:34.422
It's not your fault

26:35.867 --> 26:39.673
that your girlfriend
was in the wrong place

26:39.698 --> 26:41.341
at the wrong time.

26:43.664 --> 26:45.226
- [Theodore]- She thought
I was cheating on her.

26:49.827 --> 26:51.160
- You don't know that.

26:51.977 --> 26:53.843
When your parents passed on

26:54.757 --> 26:59.686
I wanted you to find
love, have a family.

27:00.913 --> 27:03.780
But the girl you fell
in love with is gone.

27:04.688 --> 27:10.051
You can't just replace her
with her sister.

27:11.547 --> 27:12.547
- [Theodore]- Anna?

27:15.822 --> 27:17.155
- Go to bed, Aunt Kay.

27:19.908 --> 27:23.174
Everything is going to be
alright in the morning.

